name: Large Brown Bohemian Teardrop Earrings
description:
Dimensions: 4" x 2"

This amazing pair of 3 Bohemian teardrop earrings with stainless steel earwires has a lovely pattern of black and copper seed beads that descend into larger black and amber seed beads, flowing into brown stones and brown horn-shaped beads. A beautiful addition to any collection.

name: Purple Lantern Asian-Inspired Earrings
description:
Dimensions: 3.25" in length

These vibrant and unique earrings have beautiful purple lantern handblown glass beads. Within the focal bead is a white leaf pattern. 

From the top, the design starts with a black seed bead and continues downward into a small round clear glass bead, trickling downward into a square clear glass bead and coming to a large oval dark purple matte finished bead, capped off with a flat black glossy bead. 

At the point of juncture between the body and the dangling portion, there is a small black seed bead, followed by a flat silver bead with an etched design, flowing into a bright and shiny spherical purple bead, then coming to rest on the lantern bead. Perfect for any time of year.

name: Metalwork & Threaded Heart Pendant Necklace
description:
This is the first of many necklaces in our new Mended Hearts Collection. Completely handcrafted by Laura, the lightweight frame of a heart made from copper wire is basket-woven with black thread and enveloped with a copper-wire woven finish, capturing the imperfections and beauty of love.

The double reinforced cord is long lasting and beautifully crimped with 2" spacing.

Dimensions: 

Cord Length: 16" end-to-end / 8" around the neck
Heart Pendant: 1.5" x 1.75"

name: Hand-Etched Love Peace Freedom Charm Bracelet
description:
Dimensions: Pendants: .75" in diameter
                        Cords: 2.5" in length (can stretch to 3.25")

This lovely charm bracelet is actually three individual bracelets that, when joined together, harmoniously conveys the message of Love, Peace, and Freedom, values for which the U.S.A. has stood for for centuries. 

The Love bracelet has beautiful red, hand-painted with glittering gold paint, small red glass beads, and silver beads. Red, being the color of love.

The Peace bracelet has small white pearls and white shells, chiseled into squares, and silver beads. White, giving off the serenity and vibe of peace.

The Freedom bracelet has powder blue polished glass cylindrical beads, small black spherical beads, and silver beads. Blue, conveying the freedom of the sky, and all of the possibilities in this world.

All of the charms are hand-etched with each word. All of the colors together will make anyone feel Patriotic and the message is so strong and unites all of us in three simple, yet powerful words.

The cords are all made from black stretch cord to fit most wrists.

name: Silver-Black Spiral Metalwork Necklace & Earrings Set
description:
Dimensions:  Necklace
                         - cord: 20" in length (10" worn)
                         - center spiral pendant: .75" in diameter
                         - side spiral pendants: .5" in diameter

                         Earrings
                         - 2.5" in length
                         - spiral pendants: .5" in diameter

This is the first necklace and earrings set that we have ever done. The unique and handcrafted copper wire spiraled pendants are what ties this set together. There are three of these spiral pieces on the necklace and each of the earrings has one. Along with those centerpieces is an elegant and beautifully constructed pattern of black and silver beads, with decorative pewter beads intermittently placed throughout the design. The earrings bear the same design and this amazing set will make a beautiful accessory to any outfit, any occasion, any time of year.

Necklace cord is black stretch cord and stainless steel clasp. Earrings have stainless steel earwires and are lightweight.
